OL,4,C'standstill' after strike announced
OL,6,FRubbish will be left "piling up" in
OL,7,FSheffield after workers voted to
OL,8,Fstrike, a union has warned.
OL,10,FUnite says almost 100 workers will
OL,11,Fwalk out this month over claims the
OL,12,Funion is being prevented from acting
OL,13,Fon behalf of members in negotiations
OL,14,Fwith the company.
OL,16,FIts leaders say they speak for 80% of
OL,17,Fthe workforce, but refuse collection
OL,18,Fcompany Veolia recognises another
OL,19,Funion as the employees' sole
OL,20,Frepresentative.
