OL,3,CBin collections to come to
OL,4,C'standstill' after strike announced
OL,6,FThey said collections would come to a
OL,7,F"standstill" when drivers and loaders
OL,8,Fwalk out from 29 July to 2 August.
OL,10,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,11,Fsaid: "It is absurd that a union
OL,12,Frepresenting 80% of a workforce is
OL,13,Fblocked from making collective
OL,14,Fbargaining arrangements by an
OL,15,Femployer, especially one it has
OL,16,Fnational agreements with up and down
OL,17,Fthe country.
